creator: Earl Derr Biggers
description:
LibriVox recording of Love Insurance by Earl Derr Biggers.
Read in English by Linda Andrus; Garren Grimring; ToddHW; Anusha Iyer; TriciaG; Stephen Perry

A young man came to Lloyds of London. He knew they took out policies on unusual risks... And what he wanted was love insurance. What follows is a comic novel, by the creator of the Chinese detective - Charlie Chan! - Summary by Linda Andrus

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
subject: librivox; audiobooks;comedy; romance; Mystery; honor; love
title: Love Insurance

reviews.reviewbody:
Much of the action in this fun story takes place in a Florida town called San Marco, but very obviously St. Augustine. Being a Florida history buff this gave particular interest to me. I had not read this author before, but really enjoyed his humor.

The story is read by several volunteers. All of them did well.
